data.description: Lovingly cared for, this house is ready for the new owner/occupant. Reap the benefits of care given to this property by the current owner.  Newer Trane HAVC and new refrigerator to accompany the other stainless steel appliances. Location is so very private.  Joy riders will not be cruising the block on this street which cul-de-sacs shortly after this house. The quiet is very obvious as one enjoys the rear yard currently buffered by woods. This ALL BRICK house exudes low maintenance. The abundance of windows make this a very open and naturally lit house. The features check all the boxes. Does your features list include Brazilian cherry wood floors?  If not add it! This house includes that in the living room and dining room.  Three bedrooms and 2 baths, living room and sunroom, breakfast area and formal dining. All major appliances included, even a washer & dryer. The landscape is graced with a palm tree in the front and one in the rear yard. The split floor plan places the primary bedroom close to the garage entrance, laundry and the kitchen. The accompanying bath features a double vanity, a jetted tub and a separate shower.  The large walk-in closet is double rodded to expand hanging space. Walking to the other side of the house one will catch more treasures - the two remaining bedrooms with the same naturally bright feel. Between the two bedrooms is a full bath for super convenience! This house is superbly built as the builder closely worked with the first owner/occupant.  One simply feels the structural integrity walking through the house. Ready for the next occupant, check out this gem which shines as you walk through the property.
